data.description: This updated and well-kept home in an established area is great for a young family or even retirees. With almost a quarter acre lot and many beautiful tall trees, there is plenty of room to add on to create the yard of your dreams.   The property has great access to all schools, is convenient to highways and is less than a five-minute drive to Eagle Mountain Lake.  Home also has a great storage building in back with a Pit own porch - Super Cute Home, please come and see!
